title: Lambo's field goal as time expires lifts Bolts over Browns
text:
> Ohio Lambo's field goal as time expires lifts Bolts over Browns San Diego Chargers wide receiver Steve Johnson (11) cannot make the catch as Cleveland Browns cornerback Tramon Williams applies pressure during the first half in an NFL football game Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015, in San Diego.
